# Fix: Missing 'Progress' Component Import

The [CircleVideoComposer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoComposer.tsx) file was using the [Progress](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/hooks/useCircleVideos.ts#114-118) component but it was not imported, leading to a TypeScript error: `Cannot find name 'Progress'`.

## Changes Made

### CircleVideoComposer.tsx

- Added the missing import for the [Progress](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/hooks/useCircleVideos.ts#114-118) component:
  ```tsx
  import { Progress } from '@/components/ui/progress';
  ```

### useCircleVideos.ts

- Added missing imports from `@tanstack/react-query`:
  ```ts
  import { useQuery, useMutation, useQueryClient } from '@tanstack/react-query';
  ```

