- Confirmed that [CircleVideoCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoCard.tsx) also has the correct imports for its components (e.g., `Crown`, `Badge`, [Card](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoCard.tsx#25-143)).
